a careful selection of the historical trials is necessary to render
the exchangeability assumption for the control parameters
plausible. Pocock (1976) proposed criteria for the selection
process. Nevertheless, one has to acknowledge the possibility
of prior-data conflict. Hence we consider a robust version of
the MAP prior of Section 2.1, as
